  "translations": {
    "en": "As for the right of subjects through knowledge, know that Allah made you a caretaker through knowledge He gave you and wisdom He opened for you. If you teach well without harshness or annoyance, Allah increases His bounty. But if you withhold knowledge or are harsh when sought, Allah will strip you of knowledge and its splendour and remove your place from hearts.",
